<p>
	Server-side, 11ty's default <code>inputPathToUrl</code> resolves the
	path. Browser-side, our port looks it up in the build-time page map.
	<code>htmlBaseUrl</code> and <code>serverlessUrl</code> aren't
	exercised here — they aren't default 11ty 3.x filters — but the bundle
	ships warn-once pass-throughs for both.
</p>

